# Mail Subscription Manager - Root Context

## PROJECT OVERVIEW
Cross-platform browser extension for managing email subscriptions across Gmail, Outlook, Yahoo, etc.
Users scan their inbox once, get all subscriptions with unsubscribe links, pay $5 for lifetime unlimited access.

## GOALS
- [ ] Build cross-platform extension (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari)
- [x] Implement user authentication system
- [ ] Integrate payment gateway ($5 lifetime access)
- [x] Support multiple email providers (Gmail implemented, Outlook/Yahoo pending)
- [ ] Free tier: first 5 subscriptions, then paywall
- [x] Display unsubscribe links for each subscription
- [x] Backend API for user management and payment tracking
- [x] Scalable, maintainable architecture
- [x] Track email scan history and counts
- [x] Remove unsubscribed items from user's list

